title: Disgusted
text: This app used to be so easy and convenient. Now I‚Äôm constantly being overcharged, constantly being up charged by like 25% after booking a ride thinking I‚Äôm paying one price, only to get in my ride and see on the app that I‚Äôm being charged another!!! Then once the ride is done, hours later I‚Äôll get an notification that my ride went from 35.16 to 35.78. Uber is a ripoff, Uber is just basically stealing money from us. title: My location
text: I have been using Uber for over a month now, I always get picked up at the same place. 1 product support road Savannah ga. It's at Gulf Stream aerospace. I either get picked up at the NORTH or SOUTH GATE!!! I have plenty of times before and Uber has seen and used my location. Lately it has not been allowing my location to come up and is placing me at the savannah ga airport terminal which is a 9 min walk! I am not at the airport! It's causing me my TIME and drivers to refuse to pick me a mile away from a location y'all say I'm at but I'm not at. Stop this and fix the problem please. And there is no way the ride should jump to such a high cost in the mornings! My ride is 5 miles long! No reason why it should be anywhere near 40-50$! That's stealing.
